com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Interface IFutureId<DEVICE_ID>

  • Type Parameters:
    DEVICE_ID - - iBeacon or Eddystone ID
    All Superinterfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EddystoneFutureUID, IBeaconFutureId, SecureProfileFutureUID

    public interface IFutureId<DEVICE_ID>
extends android.os.Parcelable
    Interface for resolved device IDs from API. It consists of:

    queriedBy - device ID which was used to HTTP request
    resolved - resolved device ID
    uniqueId - unique ID of resolved device
    futureIds - set of device IDs which will be transmitted in the future
